<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a7Jul1933"><font color="red">7 July 1933</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): I have telephoned to Edmond Jaloux in Lausanne and we go there on Monday (10 July 1933) &hellip; Thanks for the E.Q. piece. Please verify it chez moi etc chez lui. Is it &lsquo;rianti&rsquo; or &lsquo;fraiches et riantes&rsquo;? &hellip; Now I shall go up and write but I have a nice old pain coming on. </div>
